<p>SPASE Resource IDs are assigned by naming authorities. In a global system naming authorities must be unique. SPASE maintains the list of naming authorities used in our community. SPASE also administraters the metadata registry containing descriptions common entities.This are available on Github and through the SPASE SMWG registry. SPASE also maintains a registry for the Heliophysics Data Environment (HPDE).</header>
